was going to get through it.

00:01:42.830 --> 00:01:45.200 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know how I was
going to get out of it.

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.330 align:middle line:10%
I really hit rock bottom.

00:01:47.330 --> 00:01:51.350 align:middle line:10%
And everything was fine
before any of that.

00:01:51.350 --> 00:01:53.780 align:middle line:84%
