day where I hit rock bottom.

00:02:04.790 --> 00:02:08.400 align:middle line:84%
And I was in my, and I remember
this like it was yesterday.

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:17.190 align:middle line:84%
And I was lying in my
bed and just crying.

00:02:17.190 --> 00:02:22.370 align:middle line:84%
Crying, crying, crying all by
myself, rolled up in a ball.

00:02:22.370 --> 00:02:26.450 align:middle line:84%
