that moment to play the victim

00:03:06.110 --> 00:03:08.805 align:middle line:90%
and just said, just cry it out.

00:03:08.805 --> 00:03:10.680 align:middle line:84%
And what's amazing by
doing that, by the way,

00:03:10.680 --> 00:03:13.490 align:middle line:84%
is that you just release
it out to the universe.

00:03:13.490 --> 00:03:16.250 align:middle line:84%
And you immediately feel
better to honor yourself

00:03:16.250 --> 00:03:17.250 align:middle line:90%
and what you're feeling.

00:03:17.250 --> 00:03:18.050 align:middle line:90%
You know what?

00:03:18.050 --> 00:03:21.740 align:middle line:84%
It's OK to feel bad when
something bad happens.

00:03:21.740 --> 00:03:23.180 align:middle line:90%
Something bad's happening.

00:03:23.180 --> 00:03:24.890 align:middle line:90%
Life is life, things happen.

00:03:24.890 --> 00:03:25.730 align:middle line:90%
So I allowed that.

00:03:25.730 --> 00:03:27.470 align:middle line:84%
