bed to the window.

00:03:40.490 --> 00:03:42.620 align:middle line:84%
And I was looking
outside the window.

00:03:42.620 --> 00:03:47.540 align:middle line:84%
And I remember there was
this beautiful maple tree.

00:03:47.540 --> 00:03:49.130 align:middle line:84%
