why this is happening,

00:03:53.180 --> 00:03:59.060 align:middle line:84%
but one thing I know for sure,
something big, something huge,

00:03:59.060 --> 00:04:04.220 align:middle line:84%
something way bigger than me
is going to come out of this,

00:04:04.220 --> 00:04:09.710 align:middle line:84%
because I'm not going through
all this crap for nothing.

00:04:09.710 --> 00:04:13.430 align:middle line:90%
And it was like a declaration.

00:04:13.430 --> 00:04:17.209 align:middle line:90%
It was an intention I sent.

00:04:17.209 --> 00:04:22.100 align:middle line:90%
I sent out to the universe.

00:04:22.100 --> 00:04:24.080 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to repeat that.

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:27.620 align:middle line:10%
Because I think it's really
important for everyone

00:04:27.620 --> 00:04:29.720 align:middle line:10%
when they're going
through a difficult time

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:33.762 align:middle line:10%
to create their own declaration
and set their intention.

00:04:33.762 --> 00:04:34.970 align:middle line:90%
I didn't do it intentionally.

00:04:34.970 --> 00:04:36.220 align:middle line:90%
That was just a natural thing.

00:04:36.220 --> 00:04:38.300 align:middle line:84%
I did, but it was the
best thing I ever did.

00:04:38.300 --> 00:04:40.430 align:middle line:84%
I don't know why
this is happening,

00:04:40.430 --> 00:04:42.950 align:middle line:84%
but one thing I know for sure,
is something big, something

00:04:42.950 --> 00:04:44.810 align:middle line:84%
huge, something
way bigger than me

00:04:44.810 --> 00:04:47.630 align:middle line:84%
is going to come out of
this, because I'm not going

00:04:47.630 --> 00:04:51.000 align:middle line:90%
through this crap for nothing.

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:52.000 align:middle line:90%
And I'm not kidding you.

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.950 align:middle line:84%
Once I did that, it was
like I sent the message out

00:04:54.950 --> 00:04:58.640 align:middle line:84%
to god, universe,
whatever you believe in,

00:04:58.640 --> 00:05:02.050 align:middle line:90%
and it got the wheels in motion.

00:05:02.050 --> 00:05:06.260 align:middle line:84%
And about a week later, I
was still in that house.

00:05:06.260 --> 00:05:09.810 align:middle line:84%
We hadn't lost it yet,
we're about to lose it.

00:05:09.810 --> 00:05:13.310 align:middle line:84%
And as I was walking up
the stairs of that house,

00:05:13.310 --> 00:05:19.250 align:middle line:84%
on the fifth step I got
a message from wherever.

00:05:19.250 --> 00:05:25.250 align:middle line:84%
And it was one word, and that
one word was, unsinkable.

00:05:25.250 --> 00:05:26.180 align:middle line:90%
And it was so random.

00:05:26.180 --> 00:05:27.620 align:middle line:84%
I remember, it so
weird, I could,

00:05:27.620 --> 00:05:31.430 align:middle line:84%
I remember actually where
I was and when it happened.

00:05:31.430 --> 00:05:34.280 align:middle line:84%
And the message came and it was
one word, it was unsinkable.

00:05:34.280 --> 00:05:35.685 align:middle line:84%
And I knew exactly
what it meant.

00:05:35.685 --> 00:05:37.310 align:middle line:84%
Wasn't like, well,
that's a weird word,

00:05:37.310 --> 00:05:38.820 align:middle line:90%
where did that come from.

00:05:38.820 --> 00:05:40.040 align:middle line:90%
And it was unsinkable.

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:43.010 align:middle line:90%
I go, oh, interesting.

00:05:43.010 --> 00:05:45.080 align:middle line:90%
I understand now.

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:46.430 align:middle line:90%
And I continued walking up.

00:05:46.430 --> 00:05:49.760 align:middle line:84%
I got to the landing and I
said, I really get it now.

00:05:49.760 --> 00:05:53.150 align:middle line:84%
I'm going through all this
stuff because my mission in life

00:05:53.150 --> 00:05:57.290 align:middle line:84%
is to help others bounce
back from difficult times.

00:05:57.290 --> 00:06:01.100 align:middle line:84%
Now get your butt in gear,
Sonia, and bounce back quickly

00:06:01.100 --> 00:06:06.110 align:middle line:84%
and turn it around so you can
go out there and teach others.

00:06:06.110 --> 00:06:08.480 align:middle line:90%
And that's what I did.

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.950 align:middle line:90%
>> Amazing.

00:06:09.950 --> 00:06:12.890 align:middle line:84%
With regards to that
moment of insight

00:06:12.890 --> 00:06:18.470 align:middle line:84%
where you turned the situation
around, my observation of that

00:06:18.470 --> 00:06:22.160 align:middle line:84%
is that you created a new sense
of meaning around something.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:26.528 align:middle line:84%
How is it that meaning can help
change the situation for people

00:06:26.528 --> 00:06:28.070 align:middle line:84%
when they're going
through something?

00:06:28.070 --> 00:06:29.900 align:middle line:84%
Because you've given
that a different meaning.

00:06:29.900 --> 00:06:30.830 align:middle line:84%
You said, well, this
is, there's going

00:06:30.830 --> 00:06:33.560 align:middle line:84%
to be something big coming out
of this, like that's a choice.

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:35.270 align:middle line:90%
>> It's a choice, definitely.

00:06:35.270 --> 00:06:38.990 align:middle line:84%
And whatever choice
you make and whatever

00:06:38.990 --> 00:06:41.960 align:middle line:84%
meaning you add to
whatever is going on,

00:06:41.960 --> 00:06:46.760 align:middle line:84%
will determine your outcome and
how quickly you bounce back.

00:06:46.760 --> 00:06:49.400 align:middle line:84%
I could have chosen something
completely opposite.

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:52.670 align:middle line:84%
My life is over, I can't believe
this, what am I going to do,

00:06:52.670 --> 00:06:56.180 align:middle line:84%
I'm such a loser, how did this
happen to me, I can't believe.

00:06:56.180 --> 00:06:58.250 align:middle line:90%
Like all these negative things.

00:06:58.250 --> 00:07:02.240 align:middle line:84%
I will never get out of this
mess and be bitter forever

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:05.150 align:middle line:84%
and ever, and we all know
people who are like that.

00:07:05.150 --> 00:07:10.490 align:middle line:84%
But that wasn't my, I
found, I found a meaning

00:07:10.490 --> 00:07:12.830 align:middle line:90%
that is bigger than me.

00:07:12.830 --> 00:07:14.870 align:middle line:84%
That was something
like it was that light

00:07:14.870 --> 00:07:17.360 align:middle line:84%
at the end of the tunnel
and it was really bright,

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:19.850 align:middle line:84%
and I knew it was there
and I needed to find

00:07:19.850 --> 00:07:22.970 align:middle line:90%
my way outside that tunnel.

00:07:22.970 --> 00:07:26.300 align:middle line:84%
And so that meaning
is really important.

00:07:26.300 --> 00:07:29.220 align:middle line:84%
And we can choose that
at any given time.

00:07:29.220 --> 00:07:31.100 align:middle line:84%
We can choose a
different meaning.

00:07:31.100 --> 00:07:34.730 align:middle line:84%
And the best way to find out you
know whether it's serving you

00:07:34.730 --> 00:07:37.800 align:middle line:90%
or not is, how do you feel.

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:39.710 align:middle line:84%
Whatever meaning
you've made it mean

00:07:39.710 --> 00:07:43.100 align:middle line:84%
or whatever meaning you
added to that situation,

00:07:43.100 --> 00:07:48.050 align:middle line:84%
does it make you feel
expanded or contracted?

00:07:48.050 --> 00:07:53.180 align:middle line:84%
And so for me, being
able to help humanity

00:07:53.180 --> 00:07:55.730 align:middle line:84%
around this, because people
are suffering everywhere,

00:07:55.730 --> 00:07:59.790 align:middle line:84%
I all of a sudden was grateful
in that moment for a little.

00:07:59.790 --> 00:08:02.390 align:middle line:84%
Like I obviously wish I
could come to this big aha

00:08:02.390 --> 00:08:03.890 align:middle line:84%
without going through
all this stuff

00:08:03.890 --> 00:08:05.150 align:middle line:90%
and be able to help people.

00:08:05.150 --> 00:08:05.950 align:middle line:90%
But you know what?

00:08:05.950 --> 00:08:08.030 align:middle line:84%
People wouldn't
listen to me if I had.

00:08:08.030 --> 00:08:10.250 align:middle line:84%
If I hadn't experienced
pain and suffering,

00:08:10.250 --> 00:08:13.490 align:middle line:84%
they would have said,
you don't understand.

00:08:13.490 --> 00:08:16.070 align:middle line:84%
So I had to go through
it to be able to do that.

00:08:16.070 --> 00:08:17.580 align:middle line:90%
I chose that.

00:08:17.580 --> 00:08:20.360 align:middle line:84%
I could have made a million
other choice choices.

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:23.090 align:middle line:84%
And anyone can choose
at any given moment

00:08:23.090 --> 00:08:25.100 align:middle line:90%
what they want it to mean.

00:08:25.100 --> 00:08:31.370 align:middle line:84%
In the end, I really
believe that you

00:08:31.370 --> 00:08:33.900 align:middle line:90%
can get through anything.

00:08:33.900 --> 00:08:39.830 align:middle line:84%
And you can turn lemonade
from lemons, if you choose to.

00:08:39.830 --> 00:08:44.330 align:middle line:84%
Or you could take those lemons
and just keep them as lemons.

00:08:44.330 --> 00:08:47.710 align:middle line:90%


00:08:47.710 --> 00:08:49.930 align:middle line:84%
>> The thing about your
transformation that I find

00:08:49.930 --> 00:08:54.160 align:middle line:84%
