the first steps was this huge

00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:57.910 align:middle line:84%
aspirational goal in a way,
which seems unfathomable

00:08:57.910 --> 00:09:00.000 align:middle line:90%
for a lot of people.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:02.440 align:middle line:84%
How is dreaming big
such an important part

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:04.040 align:middle line:90%
of this process for you?

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:06.790 align:middle line:84%
And how can you take really, how
did you take yourself, I mean,

00:09:06.790 --> 00:09:09.230 align:middle line:84%
it was more a moment of
insight more than anything,

00:09:09.230 --> 00:09:10.030 align:middle line:90%
I would say.

00:09:10.030 --> 00:09:12.580 align:middle line:84%
Like some sort of divine insight
that helped you see this.

00:09:12.580 --> 00:09:16.150 align:middle line:84%
But how do you take people from
being stuck to dreaming big?

00:09:16.150 --> 00:09:18.220 align:middle line:84%
And how is dreaming
big and important part

00:09:18.220 --> 00:09:20.440 align:middle line:84%
of going through a
difficult challenge?

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:23.200 align:middle line:84%
>> You know, it's interesting,
because it's even,

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:27.940 align:middle line:84%
it sounds very evolved and
oh, I got this message.

00:09:27.940 --> 00:09:31.120 align:middle line:84%
But in reality, if you really
analyze this and break it down,

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:36.250 align:middle line:84%
it was really more, it
was more out of spite.

00:09:36.250 --> 00:09:38.110 align:middle line:84%
It was more out of,
oh yeah, well, I'm

00:09:38.110 --> 00:09:40.510 align:middle line:84%
not going through this
stuff for nothing.

00:09:40.510 --> 00:09:41.650 align:middle line:90%
I'll show you.

00:09:41.650 --> 00:09:42.910 align:middle line:90%
Who, I don't know.

00:09:42.910 --> 00:09:44.043 align:middle line:90%
Seriously.

00:09:44.043 --> 00:09:45.460 align:middle line:84%
But it was more
out of that, where

00:09:45.460 --> 00:09:47.440 align:middle line:84%
it's like, oh my goodness,
this just happened.

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:49.090 align:middle line:84%
How am I going to
get out of this?

00:09:49.090 --> 00:09:49.890 align:middle line:90%
You know what?

00:09:49.890 --> 00:09:52.870 align:middle line:84%
I'm not going through all this
stuff for nothing, no way.

00:09:52.870 --> 00:09:55.480 align:middle line:90%


00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:59.710 align:middle line:84%
And then the universe,
god, whatever, said, OK.

00:09:59.710 --> 00:10:03.880 align:middle line:10%
And so from dreaming big, what's
interesting about dreaming big,

