even that seemed crazy
when I said well,

00:10:06.820 --> 00:10:08.770 align:middle line:10%
my mission now is to
help people bounce back

00:10:08.770 --> 00:10:11.960 align:middle line:10%
from difficult times.

00:10:11.960 --> 00:10:13.610 align:middle line:84%
I said that, I made
that statement,

00:10:13.610 --> 00:10:15.143 align:middle line:84%
but I didn't know
what that meant.

00:10:15.143 --> 00:10:16.810 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know what
that would look like.

00:10:16.810 --> 00:10:20.650 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know where
it would take me.

00:10:20.650 --> 00:10:22.585 align:middle line:84%
It wasn't like I said
this and I'm like,

00:10:22.585 --> 00:10:24.460 align:middle line:84%
oh, and I know exactly
how I'm going to do it

00:10:24.460 --> 00:10:26.502 align:middle line:84%
and the next week everyone's
going to bounce back

00:10:26.502 --> 00:10:28.880 align:middle line:84%
and it's all done and
I'll have my book written.

00:10:28.880 --> 00:10:29.680 align:middle line:90%
I just said that.

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:32.290 align:middle line:84%
It was, sometimes you
need to set a goal

00:10:32.290 --> 00:10:34.480 align:middle line:90%
or create that dream.

00:10:34.480 --> 00:10:37.000 align:middle line:90%
You don't need to know the how.

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:40.540 align:middle line:84%
Just first get the
dream together.

00:10:40.540 --> 00:10:43.300 align:middle line:84%
And what I always say
is, pick that dream.

00:10:43.300 --> 00:10:46.270 align:middle line:84%
So if you're having
financial problems,

00:10:46.270 --> 00:10:50.110 align:middle line:84%
how much money would you like
to make in the next year?

00:10:50.110 --> 00:10:53.630 align:middle line:84%
And you come up with
an amount in your mind.

00:10:53.630 --> 00:10:54.880 align:middle line:90%
And what I always say is this.

00:10:54.880 --> 00:10:57.610 align:middle line:84%
Once you've picked
that amount, you

00:10:57.610 --> 00:11:03.730 align:middle line:84%
have an amount picked in
your mind, times it by 10.

00:11:03.730 --> 00:11:06.010 align:middle line:90%
And everyone's, oh, my goodness!

00:11:06.010 --> 00:11:07.740 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to make
a million dollars?

00:11:07.740 --> 00:11:09.430 align:middle line:90%
You know, that kind of thing.

00:11:09.430 --> 00:11:11.110 align:middle line:84%
And it's like yeah,
and why didn't you

00:11:11.110 --> 00:11:14.890 align:middle line:90%
pick that amount to begin with?

00:11:14.890 --> 00:11:18.790 align:middle line:84%
And it's because we have
difficulty dreaming big.

00:11:18.790 --> 00:11:23.440 align:middle line:84%
And often, we are the ones
that are our own obstacles

00:11:23.440 --> 00:11:26.260 align:middle line:90%
in our own way.

00:11:26.260 --> 00:11:30.260 align:middle line:84%
And whatever your
dreams are, when

00:11:30.260 --> 00:11:32.710 align:middle line:84%
you're able to create
your big dreams,

00:11:32.710 --> 00:11:36.340 align:middle line:84%
once you've decided on
that, then the opportunities

00:11:36.340 --> 00:11:38.570 align:middle line:84%
and the ideas start
coming to you.

00:11:38.570 --> 00:11:41.470 align:middle line:84%
So if your goal
was $100,000, you

00:11:41.470 --> 00:11:44.230 align:middle line:84%
would then have ideas
and opportunities

00:11:44.230 --> 00:11:47.350 align:middle line:90%
that are $100,000 worth.

00:11:47.350 --> 00:11:49.510 align:middle line:84%
If you have a goal
of a million dollars,

00:11:49.510 --> 00:11:51.427 align:middle line:84%
you will have ideas
and opportunities

00:11:51.427 --> 00:11:53.260 align:middle line:84%
that come to you that
are a million dollars.

00:11:53.260 --> 00:11:56.500 align:middle line:84%
Because your brain is
thinking at a different level.

00:11:56.500 --> 00:11:59.985 align:middle line:84%
When I decided I wanted to make
my first million, I remember,

00:11:59.985 --> 00:12:01.360 align:middle line:84%
this is how I was
going to do it.

00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:02.800 align:middle line:84%
This isn't how it
happened, but I

00:12:02.800 --> 00:12:06.040 align:middle line:84%
started coming up with
ideas, which I would never

00:12:06.040 --> 00:12:09.598 align:middle line:84%
have come up with if my goal
was $50,000 or $100,000.

00:12:09.598 --> 00:12:11.140 align:middle line:84%
So I wanted to make
my first million.

00:12:11.140 --> 00:12:12.370 align:middle line:84%
I said, I know how
I'm going to do it.

00:12:12.370 --> 00:12:14.417 align:middle line:84%
Because I didn't know any
other way, by the way.

00:12:14.417 --> 00:12:16.000 align:middle line:10%
And by the way,
there's a million ways

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:18.730 align:middle line:10%
to make a million
dollars, if not more.

00:12:18.730 --> 00:12:20.080 align:middle line:10%
That's what I always say.

00:12:20.080 --> 00:12:23.680 align:middle line:10%
And my goal was, I'm going
to write a bestseller book

00:12:23.680 --> 00:12:25.800 align:middle line:10%
and I'm going to sell
a million copies.

00:12:25.800 --> 00:12:27.550 align:middle line:84%
And when you have a
publisher, you usually

00:12:27.550 --> 00:12:29.080 align:middle line:90%
get about $1 a book.

00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:31.550 align:middle line:84%
So that's how I'm going
to make a million dollars.

00:12:31.550 --> 00:12:34.180 align:middle line:84%
So I'm going to
write my first book.

00:12:34.180 --> 00:12:35.890 align:middle line:84%
Is that how I made
my first million?

00:12:35.890 --> 00:12:36.690 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:12:36.690 --> 00:12:37.810 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:12:37.810 --> 00:12:40.750 align:middle line:84%
But at least I had an
idea and it started

00:12:40.750 --> 00:12:42.850 align:middle line:90%
making me think in that way.

00:12:42.850 --> 00:12:44.710 align:middle line:90%
Yes, I wrote a bestseller.

00:12:44.710 --> 00:12:47.110 align:middle line:84%
No, I didn't make a
million dollars that way.

00:12:47.110 --> 00:12:50.710 align:middle line:84%
But I came up with all
different other ideas.

00:12:50.710 --> 00:12:56.950 align:middle line:84%
And so many things just started
arriving and landing in my lap,

00:12:56.950 --> 00:12:59.710 align:middle line:84%
because my mind now
was starting to look

00:12:59.710 --> 00:13:02.680 align:middle line:90%
for things in that area.

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:05.290 align:middle line:84%
So you become, once you
have that really big goal,

00:13:05.290 --> 00:13:09.190 align:middle line:84%
then you become more
aware, more alert.

00:13:09.190 --> 00:13:10.690 align:middle line:84%
Once you're looking
out that window,

00:13:10.690 --> 00:13:12.980 align:middle line:84%
you're seeing what
you're looking for,

00:13:12.980 --> 00:13:14.830 align:middle line:84%
which is how to make
a million dollars,

00:13:14.830 --> 00:13:19.540 align:middle line:84%
how to find my soulmate, how
to have the dream career.

00:13:19.540 --> 00:13:23.170 align:middle line:84%
All those things all of a
sudden start showing up for you.

00:13:23.170 --> 00:13:28.600 align:middle line:84%
It's when you get stuck
in that negative space

00:13:28.600 --> 00:13:31.090 align:middle line:84%
that you don't see
the opportunities.

00:13:31.090 --> 00:13:34.450 align:middle line:84%
You're in this dark fog,
you're in that tunnel.

00:13:34.450 --> 00:13:36.980 align:middle line:84%
There could be a million
doors of opportunities

00:13:36.980 --> 00:13:37.780 align:middle line:90%
all around you.

00:13:37.780 --> 00:13:40.330 align:middle line:90%
You will never see them.

00:13:40.330 --> 00:13:42.950 align:middle line:84%
You will never see them,
because you're stuck.

00:13:42.950 --> 00:13:43.750 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:13:43.750 --> 00:13:47.860 align:middle line:84%
I always say when
you are stuck, it's

00:13:47.860 --> 00:13:51.190 align:middle line:84%
like you are staring
at a closed door.

00:13:51.190 --> 00:13:54.280 align:middle line:84%
Not only is it closed,
but it's locked.

00:13:54.280 --> 00:13:57.160 align:middle line:90%
And you're not going anywhere.

00:13:57.160 --> 00:14:00.070 align:middle line:84%
And what I mean by that, is
anytime you're complaining,

00:14:00.070 --> 00:14:02.800 align:middle line:84%
anytime you are feeling
sorry for yourself,

00:14:02.800 --> 00:14:04.900 align:middle line:84%
anytime you're saying,
why is this happening,

00:14:04.900 --> 00:14:07.930 align:middle line:84%
I can't believe this is
happening, this isn't fair,

00:14:07.930 --> 00:14:12.080 align:middle line:84%
and all that resentment and
anger around your situation,

00:14:12.080 --> 00:14:16.390 align:middle line:84%
it's hard to move past that and
actually bounce back quickly,

00:14:16.390 --> 00:14:17.890 align:middle line:90%
and bounce back big.

00:14:17.890 --> 00:14:20.590 align:middle line:84%
It's really difficult.
Because you're just busy

00:14:20.590 --> 00:14:22.690 align:middle line:90%
staring at this closed door.

00:14:22.690 --> 00:14:26.140 align:middle line:84%
Meanwhile, there are all these
open doors all around you,

00:14:26.140 --> 00:14:28.390 align:middle line:84%
but you don't see
them, because I'm

00:14:28.390 --> 00:14:30.580 align:middle line:84%
too busy staring at
this closed door that's

00:14:30.580 --> 00:14:32.890 align:middle line:90%
right in front of your face.

00:14:32.890 --> 00:14:36.580 align:middle line:84%
And so what I say is, step
away from that closed door.

00:14:36.580 --> 00:14:39.250 align:middle line:84%
Stop focusing on all the
negative and all the things

00:14:39.250 --> 00:14:41.200 align:middle line:90%
that you're not happy about.

00:14:41.200 --> 00:14:42.970 align:middle line:84%
And start focusing
on what you want

00:14:42.970 --> 00:14:44.890 align:middle line:84%
and what you want to
create into your life,

00:14:44.890 --> 00:14:48.490 align:middle line:84%
like what you want to
bring into your life.

00:14:48.490 --> 00:14:50.320 align:middle line:90%
Focus on the positive.

00:14:50.320 --> 00:14:52.480 align:middle line:84%
And as soon as you start
focusing on the positive

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:56.140 align:middle line:84%
and what you want to create
and dream big, all of a sudden

00:14:56.140 --> 00:14:58.120 align:middle line:84%
you step away and
you look around

00:14:58.120 --> 00:15:00.710 align:middle line:84%
and you say, oh my goodness,
where were all these open doors

00:15:00.710 --> 00:15:01.510 align:middle line:90%
before?

00:15:01.510 --> 00:15:02.310 align:middle line:90%
You know what?

00:15:02.310 --> 00:15:04.600 align:middle line:84%
They were they're
all along, right?

00:15:04.600 --> 00:15:07.240 align:middle line:84%
It's what you look for
is what you will find.

00:15:07.240 --> 00:15:08.710 align:middle line:84%
And if you're
constantly negative,

00:15:08.710 --> 00:15:10.000 align:middle line:90%
you'll find more negativity.

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:11.417 align:middle line:84%
If you're constantly
positive, you

00:15:11.417 --> 00:15:15.490 align:middle line:84%
will always find all the
positive things all around you.

00:15:15.490 --> 00:15:18.520 align:middle line:84%
So it's one of those things that
once you start becoming aware

00:15:18.520 --> 00:15:23.740 align:middle line:84%
what's in there and what's going
on and be able to shift that,

00:15:23.740 --> 00:15:26.710 align:middle line:90%
your entire life will shift.

00:15:26.710 --> 00:15:28.660 align:middle line:84%
You know, I talk
about reprogramming

00:15:28.660 --> 00:15:30.730 align:middle line:90%
your conscious mind.

00:15:30.730 --> 00:15:34.850 align:middle line:84%
And I usually break it
down into three steps.

00:15:34.850 --> 00:15:37.510 align:middle line:84%
And the first one is
reprogram your conscious mind.

00:15:37.510 --> 00:15:41.620 align:middle line:84%
And what your conscious mind
is, is all about your thoughts

00:15:41.620 --> 00:15:43.210 align:middle line:90%
and what you're thinking.

00:15:43.210 --> 00:15:47.600 align:middle line:84%
Now I honest, for me personally,
many, many years ago,

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:51.340 align:middle line:84%
I used to be the biggest
drama queen on the planet.

00:15:51.340 --> 00:15:54.370 align:middle line:84%
Now you imagine the
most negative person

00:15:54.370 --> 00:15:57.337 align:middle line:84%
you know who's the biggest
drama queen on the planet,

00:15:57.337 --> 00:15:58.420 align:middle line:90%
just think of that person.

00:15:58.420 --> 00:16:00.040 align:middle line:84%
Times that by
1,000, that was me.

00:16:00.040 --> 00:16:00.840 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:16:00.840 --> 00:16:04.060 align:middle line:84%
I can promise you, that's
how bad I used to be.

00:16:04.060 --> 00:16:06.460 align:middle line:90%
Until one day I got a big aha.

00:16:06.460 --> 00:16:09.590 align:middle line:84%
And I was at an event and
they were talking about this.

00:16:09.590 --> 00:16:11.410 align:middle line:84%
And I walked out of
there with a light bulb

00:16:11.410 --> 00:16:15.250 align:middle line:84%
on the top of my head,
realizing oh my goodness,

00:16:15.250 --> 00:16:17.990 align:middle line:90%
are you kidding me.

00:16:17.990 --> 00:16:20.455 align:middle line:84%
I've been creating my own
suffering all this time?

00:16:20.455 --> 00:16:22.960 align:middle line:90%


00:16:22.960 --> 00:16:24.190 align:middle line:90%
I just couldn't believe it.

00:16:24.190 --> 00:16:26.620 align:middle line:84%
And the exciting part was,
well, that's a good thing,

00:16:26.620 --> 00:16:29.210 align:middle line:84%
because that means
I can change it.

00:16:29.210 --> 00:16:31.420 align:middle line:90%
I'm no longer a victim.

00:16:31.420 --> 00:16:33.610 align:middle line:84%
And so when I say reprogram
your conscious mind,

00:16:33.610 --> 00:16:36.010 align:middle line:84%
I'm talking about your thoughts
and what you're thinking.

00:16:36.010 --> 00:16:37.570 align:middle line:90%
So let me explain.

00:16:37.570 --> 00:16:38.860 align:middle line:90%
The way it works is this.

00:16:38.860 --> 00:16:41.330 align:middle line:84%
Is that when something negative
is happening around you,

00:16:41.330 --> 00:16:43.750 align:middle line:84%
so it's let's say,
outside of you,

00:16:43.750 --> 00:16:48.580 align:middle line:84%
and it could be in my case,
I was $124,000 in debt,

00:16:48.580 --> 00:16:52.620 align:middle line:84%
my relationship was breaking
up, my ex was an alcoholic,

00:16:52.620 --> 00:16:54.977 align:middle line:84%
I had serious health issues,
we were losing our home.

00:16:54.977 --> 00:16:56.560 align:middle line:84%
All these things
were happening to me.

00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:58.930 align:middle line:84%
All these things
were happening to me

00:16:58.930 --> 00:17:03.160 align:middle line:84%
and I was feeling really sad,
depressed, angry, resentful,

00:17:03.160 --> 00:17:04.960 align:middle line:90%
all those negative feelings.

00:17:04.960 --> 00:17:07.865 align:middle line:84%
And so if somebody would
have asked me and said, well,

00:17:07.865 --> 00:17:09.490 align:middle line:84%
why are you feeling
all those feelings?

00:17:09.490 --> 00:17:10.390 align:middle line:90%
Why are you feeling sad?

00:17:10.390 --> 00:17:11.319 align:middle line:90%
Why are you feeling angry?

00:17:11.319 --> 00:17:12.569 align:middle line:90%
Why are you feeling resentful?

00:17:12.569 --> 00:17:14.250 align:middle line:90%
What is all this negativity?

00:17:14.250 --> 00:17:15.970 align:middle line:90%
I'm saying, why?

00:17:15.970 --> 00:17:19.990 align:middle line:84%
Because I'm losing my home,
$124,000 in debt, my ex,

00:17:19.990 --> 00:17:22.720 align:middle line:84%
at the time, he wasn't
my ex, is an alcoholic, I

00:17:22.720 --> 00:17:25.089 align:middle line:90%
have serious health challenge.

00:17:25.089 --> 00:17:26.530 align:middle line:90%
Of course I'm feeling this way.

00:17:26.530 --> 00:17:28.130 align:middle line:90%
That's why I feel this way.

00:17:28.130 --> 00:17:28.930 align:middle line:90%
But you know what?

00:17:28.930 --> 00:17:31.690 align:middle line:90%
That's not true.

00:17:31.690 --> 00:17:35.110 align:middle line:84%
So you have something outside
of you that's happening.

00:17:35.110 --> 00:17:37.570 align:middle line:84%
Financial,
relationship, whatever,

00:17:37.570 --> 00:17:39.340 align:middle line:90%
and you feel something.

00:17:39.340 --> 00:17:41.720 align:middle line:84%
You assume that the
reason you feel this way

00:17:41.720 --> 00:17:42.520 align:middle line:90%
is because of that.

00:17:42.520 --> 00:17:43.990 align:middle line:90%
But that isn't true.

00:17:43.990 --> 00:17:46.690 align:middle line:84%
Something happens
between that and this.

00:17:46.690 --> 00:17:49.070 align:middle line:90%
Something here happens.

00:17:49.070 --> 00:17:52.840 align:middle line:84%
And what happens is, you
have a thought about what's

00:17:52.840 --> 00:17:54.730 align:middle line:90%
happening in your life.

00:17:54.730 --> 00:17:57.970 align:middle line:84%
That thought is causing
you to feel the way you do.

00:17:57.970 --> 00:18:01.870 align:middle line:84%
So you are causing your
own pain and suffering.

00:18:01.870 --> 00:18:03.060 align:middle line:90%
It's not out there.

00:18:03.060 --> 00:18:04.810 align:middle line:84%
And the reason that's
true, is because you

00:18:04.810 --> 00:18:07.900 align:middle line:84%
can have 10 people going
through the exact same situation

00:18:07.900 --> 00:18:11.120 align:middle line:90%
and have 10 different reactions.

00:18:11.120 --> 00:18:11.920 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:18:11.920 --> 00:18:15.490 align:middle line:84%
And so if that's the case,
then what's the difference?

00:18:15.490 --> 00:18:17.200 align:middle line:90%
It's what you think.

00:18:17.200 --> 00:18:19.870 align:middle line:84%
So whenever you're going through
a difficult time in your life

00:18:19.870 --> 00:18:22.120 align:middle line:84%
and you're not feeling good,
you have to ask yourself,

00:18:22.120 --> 00:18:24.160 align:middle line:84%
OK, obviously
something's happening

00:18:24.160 --> 00:18:27.550 align:middle line:84%
and things happen in life
and we have to deal with it

00:18:27.550 --> 00:18:31.670 align:middle line:84%
and get through it, get back
up, move forward, handle it.

00:18:31.670 --> 00:18:33.530 align:middle line:90%
How quickly you do that is this.

00:18:33.530 --> 00:18:36.490 align:middle line:84%
And so what happens
is, you have to ask

00:18:36.490 --> 00:18:38.448 align:middle line:84%
yourself that question
in those situations

00:18:38.448 --> 00:18:39.490 align:middle line:90%
when you don't feel good.

00:18:39.490 --> 00:18:41.620 align:middle line:90%
And the question is this.

00:18:41.620 --> 00:18:43.090 align:middle line:84%
What am I thinking
about right now

00:18:43.090 --> 00:18:46.180 align:middle line:90%
that's making me feel this way?

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:50.860 align:middle line:84%
And the stories
we tell ourselves.

00:18:50.860 --> 00:18:53.890 align:middle line:84%
You wouldn't even talk
to your, you know,

00:18:53.890 --> 00:18:57.310 align:middle line:84%
like your worst enemy the
way we talk to ourselves.

00:18:57.310 --> 00:18:59.980 align:middle line:84%
And of course, and
you'll, do that exercise.

00:18:59.980 --> 00:19:02.320 align:middle line:84%
I mean, to this day,
I still do that.

00:19:02.320 --> 00:19:04.900 align:middle line:84%
If I feel like I'm getting
upset or stressed or anything,

00:19:04.900 --> 00:19:05.870 align:middle line:90%
I will ask myself.

00:19:05.870 --> 00:19:07.600 align:middle line:90%
I say, wow, I do not feel good.

00:19:07.600 --> 00:19:08.920 align:middle line:90%
I need to stop for a second.

00:19:08.920 --> 00:19:10.140 align:middle line:90%
What is going on right now?

00:19:10.140 --> 00:19:12.490 align:middle line:90%
What am I thinking right now?

00:19:12.490 --> 00:19:15.850 align:middle line:84%
And then I go over the story
I've been telling myself.

00:19:15.850 --> 00:19:17.890 align:middle line:84%
And I realize, oh,
well that makes sense.

00:19:17.890 --> 00:19:20.570 align:middle line:90%
Now let's change the story.

00:19:20.570 --> 00:19:21.370 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:19:21.370 --> 00:19:24.500 align:middle line:84%
Because often, it's just a
story and your interpretation

00:19:24.500 --> 00:19:25.300 align:middle line:90%
of what's going on.

00:19:25.300 --> 00:19:27.758 align:middle line:84%
Well, what if you could actually
change that interpretation

00:19:27.758 --> 00:19:29.080 align:middle line:90%
to something positive?

00:19:29.080 --> 00:19:31.320 align:middle line:84%
Because in the end, think
about, think about this.

00:19:31.320 --> 00:19:33.070 align:middle line:84%
Think about something
that happened to you

00:19:33.070 --> 00:19:35.320 align:middle line:90%
in the past that was negative.

00:19:35.320 --> 00:19:38.590 align:middle line:84%
And then fast forward two years,
five years, and you look back

00:19:38.590 --> 00:19:41.738 align:middle line:84%
and you most of the
time you would say,

00:19:41.738 --> 00:19:43.780 align:middle line:84%
that was the best thing
that ever happened to me.

00:19:43.780 --> 00:19:45.250 align:middle line:84%
Could have been a
breakup, and then

00:19:45.250 --> 00:19:48.160 align:middle line:84%
you later met your
real soulmate.

00:19:48.160 --> 00:19:50.620 align:middle line:84%
In my case, all those
things happened, and today,

00:19:50.620 --> 00:19:52.090 align:middle line:90%
look at what I'm doing.

00:19:52.090 --> 00:19:55.760 align:middle line:84%
Like if somebody gave me
a crystal ball and said,

00:19:55.760 --> 00:19:57.370 align:middle line:84%
OK, Sonia, I know
you're depressed

00:19:57.370 --> 00:20:00.280 align:middle line:84%
and crying and playing the
victim and all that, OK.

00:20:00.280 --> 00:20:03.250 align:middle line:84%
Look at this, look
at this crystal ball.

00:20:03.250 --> 00:20:06.760 align:middle line:84%
Look at your life of how it's
going to be in the future.

00:20:06.760 --> 00:20:08.560 align:middle line:84%
If I looked at that,
I would have said,

00:20:08.560 --> 00:20:11.650 align:middle line:84%
I don't know whose life that is,
but there's no way it's mine,

00:20:11.650 --> 00:20:15.770 align:middle line:84%
because I have no idea
