00:20:15.770 --> 00:20:17.320 align:middle line:90%
So you never know.

00:20:17.320 --> 00:20:20.500 align:middle line:84%
You have to trust and
you have to believe,

00:20:20.500 --> 00:20:22.220 align:middle line:90%
and you move forward.

00:20:22.220 --> 00:20:24.880 align:middle line:84%
But I'm telling you, right here,
this is where it all begins.

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:26.470 align:middle line:84%
By reprogramming
your conscious mind.

00:20:26.470 --> 00:20:28.370 align:middle line:84%
Conscious mind
means your thoughts.

00:20:28.370 --> 00:20:30.760 align:middle line:84%
You can easily become aware
of what you're thinking.

00:20:30.760 --> 00:20:32.680 align:middle line:84%
As soon as you do
that and you're

00:20:32.680 --> 00:20:37.990 align:middle line:84%
able to shift it and turn it
into a positive story or a more

00:20:37.990 --> 00:20:41.050 align:middle line:90%
positive story, you feel better.

00:20:41.050 --> 00:20:43.720 align:middle line:84%
Because obviously,
your thoughts are

00:20:43.720 --> 00:20:46.390 align:middle line:84%
what's causing you to
feel what you're feeling.

00:20:46.390 --> 00:20:49.050 align:middle line:90%


00:20:49.050 --> 00:20:51.590 align:middle line:90%
>> So step one, conscious mind.

00:20:51.590 --> 00:20:55.220 align:middle line:84%
Interrupt those thoughts,
question those thoughts,

00:20:55.220 --> 00:20:58.460 align:middle line:84%
try to do some discovery
around why do I,

00:20:58.460 --> 00:21:00.363 align:middle line:84%
why am I feeling
bad about this and

00:21:00.363 --> 00:21:01.530 align:middle line:90%
can I change those thoughts?

00:21:01.530 --> 00:21:03.080 align:middle line:90%
So that makes sense.

00:21:03.080 --> 00:21:05.000 align:middle line:90%
I can understand that.

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:06.360 align:middle line:90%
Step two, step three.

00:21:06.360 --> 00:21:07.160 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:21:07.160 --> 00:21:10.800 align:middle line:84%
So step two is reprogram
your subconscious mind.

00:21:10.800 --> 00:21:14.660 align:middle line:84%
So what that means is, this
is a lot harder by the way.

00:21:14.660 --> 00:21:16.790 align:middle line:84%
You can do it, it's just
harder than, the other one

00:21:16.790 --> 00:21:18.648 align:middle line:84%
is like, what am I
thinking about right now

00:21:18.648 --> 00:21:19.940 align:middle line:90%
that's making me feel this way.

00:21:19.940 --> 00:21:20.960 align:middle line:90%
Pretty simple.

00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:24.020 align:middle line:84%
Step two, subconscious,
reprogram your subconscious

00:21:24.020 --> 00:21:28.910 align:middle line:84%
mind, those are your
limiting beliefs.

00:21:28.910 --> 00:21:33.750 align:middle line:84%
What you believe is
what you will manifest.

00:21:33.750 --> 00:21:34.550 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:21:34.550 --> 00:21:37.970 align:middle line:84%
And so you have to figure
out that area of your life

00:21:37.970 --> 00:21:42.110 align:middle line:84%
that isn't working, what are
your beliefs around that area?

00:21:42.110 --> 00:21:45.920 align:middle line:84%
Because those beliefs will
determine how successful you

00:21:45.920 --> 00:21:48.558 align:middle line:90%
are in that area of your life.

00:21:48.558 --> 00:21:50.600 align:middle line:84%
And it's really interesting,
because sometimes we

00:21:50.600 --> 00:21:54.178 align:middle line:84%
have beliefs and we don't even
know we have those beliefs.

00:21:54.178 --> 00:21:56.720 align:middle line:84%
And that's why that's step one
is important, because once you

00:21:56.720 --> 00:21:58.350 align:middle line:84%
start becoming aware
of your thoughts,

00:21:58.350 --> 00:22:00.683 align:middle line:84%
then you start recognizing
what you're telling yourself.

00:22:00.683 --> 00:22:03.770 align:middle line:84%
What you're telling yourself
is so powerful in determining

00:22:03.770 --> 00:22:08.690 align:middle line:84%
what action you take,
determining of what direction

00:22:08.690 --> 00:22:10.470 align:middle line:90%
you will go in your life.

00:22:10.470 --> 00:22:13.040 align:middle line:84%
And so your limiting
beliefs are what

00:22:13.040 --> 00:22:17.630 align:middle line:84%
really drive you in every way
without you even realizing it.

00:22:17.630 --> 00:22:20.150 align:middle line:84%
The good news is,
that you can uncover

00:22:20.150 --> 00:22:21.510 align:middle line:90%
what your limiting beliefs are.

00:22:21.510 --> 00:22:23.930 align:middle line:84%
And once you, in that
area that's not working,

00:22:23.930 --> 00:22:26.090 align:middle line:84%
and once you do, then
you just shift them

00:22:26.090 --> 00:22:29.240 align:middle line:84%
to positive empowering
beliefs instead.

00:22:29.240 --> 00:22:33.080 align:middle line:84%
And then once you've done that,
everything shifts in that area.

00:22:33.080 --> 00:22:35.630 align:middle line:84%
But until you do
that, it'll be very

00:22:35.630 --> 00:22:39.260 align:middle line:84%
difficult to truly transform
that area of your life.

00:22:39.260 --> 00:22:42.085 align:middle line:84%
You might say, I want
to meet my soul mate.

00:22:42.085 --> 00:22:43.460 align:middle line:84%
And then you meet
your soul mate,

00:22:43.460 --> 00:22:44.960 align:middle line:84%
but then you break
up three months later

00:22:44.960 --> 00:22:46.580 align:middle line:84%
and then you're looking
for your soul mate again.

00:22:46.580 --> 00:22:48.663 align:middle line:84%
And then you meet your
soul mate six months later,

00:22:48.663 --> 00:22:51.590 align:middle line:84%
and then you break up, and
there are limiting beliefs

00:22:51.590 --> 00:22:54.500 align:middle line:84%
around that area of your
life around relationships.

00:22:54.500 --> 00:22:57.180 align:middle line:84%
Or money's a big
one for many people.

00:22:57.180 --> 00:23:00.500 align:middle line:84%
And so if you're finding you're
having a lot of difficulty

00:23:00.500 --> 00:23:03.800 align:middle line:84%
making ends meet or you're not
reaching your financial goals

00:23:03.800 --> 00:23:07.050 align:middle line:84%
and no matter how hard you
try, how harder you work,

00:23:07.050 --> 00:23:09.590 align:middle line:84%
no matter what you do,
it's still not happening,

00:23:09.590 --> 00:23:11.540 align:middle line:84%
or sometimes it happens
