00:23:11.540 --> 00:23:13.850 align:middle line:84%
and it happens and
you lose it, you

00:23:13.850 --> 00:23:16.550 align:middle line:84%
need to analyze and figure
out what your beliefs are

00:23:16.550 --> 00:23:18.830 align:middle line:90%
around the area of money.

00:23:18.830 --> 00:23:20.040 align:middle line:90%
That's a really huge one.

00:23:20.040 --> 00:23:21.498 align:middle line:84%
So what people are
normally looking

00:23:21.498 --> 00:23:23.120 align:middle line:84%
for when it comes
to making money,

00:23:23.120 --> 00:23:25.250 align:middle line:84%
is all different kinds
