00:23:25.250 --> 00:23:26.660 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to get a better job.

00:23:26.660 --> 00:23:28.280 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to start
a new business.

00:23:28.280 --> 00:23:29.250 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to do this.

00:23:29.250 --> 00:23:31.790 align:middle line:90%
And those are all good things.

00:23:31.790 --> 00:23:35.990 align:middle line:84%
But if you haven't shifted your
limiting beliefs around money,

00:23:35.990 --> 00:23:40.640 align:middle line:84%
you will always be struggling
around money, no matter what.

00:23:40.640 --> 00:23:42.320 align:middle line:84%
So the good news is,
all you have to do

00:23:42.320 --> 00:23:43.940 align:middle line:84%
is uncover what your
limiting beliefs are.

00:23:43.940 --> 00:23:45.523 align:middle line:84%
So I'm going to give
you some examples

00:23:45.523 --> 00:23:49.820 align:middle line:84%
around what limiting beliefs
