00:23:52.220 --> 00:23:55.550 align:middle line:90%
Rich people are jerks.

00:23:55.550 --> 00:24:01.970 align:middle line:90%
I'm too old to be rich.

00:24:01.970 --> 00:24:05.840 align:middle line:90%
I'm not smart enough to be rich.

00:24:05.840 --> 00:24:08.870 align:middle line:90%
Money doesn't grow on trees.

00:24:08.870 --> 00:24:10.790 align:middle line:84%
All these, whatever
your beliefs are.

00:24:10.790 --> 00:24:13.280 align:middle line:84%
And often, by the way,
where these limiting beliefs

00:24:13.280 --> 00:24:18.540 align:middle line:84%
