00:24:48.480 --> 00:24:49.910 align:middle line:90%
There was so much scarcity.

00:24:49.910 --> 00:24:52.890 align:middle line:84%
A lot of love, but
a lot of scarcity.

00:24:52.890 --> 00:24:56.720 align:middle line:84%
And so I had to deprogram
all that over time

00:24:56.720 --> 00:24:59.540 align:middle line:84%
once I started
understanding all of this.

00:24:59.540 --> 00:25:01.610 align:middle line:84%
And what's interesting
about limiting beliefs,

00:25:01.610 --> 00:25:05.600 align:middle line:84%
is that you will start
uncovering them all the time.

00:25:05.600 --> 00:25:10.670 align:middle line:84%
Even like for me,
financially, I really

00:25:10.670 --> 00:25:13.130 align:middle line:84%
figured out what all my
limiting beliefs were.

00:25:13.130 --> 00:25:16.490 align:middle line:84%
And then eventually, I realized
I still had them years later

00:25:16.490 --> 00:25:18.020 align:middle line:90%
after I was already successful.

00:25:18.020 --> 00:25:21.120 align:middle line:84%
And I'd love to
give you an example.

00:25:21.120 --> 00:25:23.150 align:middle line:84%
This is an extreme
example, but just

00:25:23.150 --> 00:25:27.500 align:middle line:84%
to give you an idea of how
powerful limiting beliefs are.

00:25:27.500 --> 00:25:30.380 align:middle line:84%
I had bounced back,
and that was great.

00:25:30.380 --> 00:25:32.940 align:middle line:84%
And my business was booming
and I was doing really well.

00:25:32.940 --> 00:25:35.660 align:middle line:84%
And I was completely out of
debt and had a nice sum of money

00:25:35.660 --> 00:25:37.040 align:middle line:90%
in my account.

00:25:37.040 --> 00:25:39.620 align:middle line:90%
And I was making six figures.

00:25:39.620 --> 00:25:42.530 align:middle line:84%
And all my colleagues
and friends

00:25:42.530 --> 00:25:44.990 align:middle line:90%
were making seven figures.

00:25:44.990 --> 00:25:50.300 align:middle line:84%
And my goal was to make seven
figures, make my first million.

00:25:50.300 --> 00:25:53.720 align:middle line:84%
And I tried and tried and I
didn't know what else to do.

00:25:53.720 --> 00:25:54.770 align:middle line:90%
It just wasn't happening.

00:25:54.770 --> 00:25:56.478 align:middle line:84%
Now I couldn't work
more hours, because I

00:25:56.478 --> 00:25:58.250 align:middle line:90%
was working so many hours.

00:25:58.250 --> 00:26:00.170 align:middle line:84%
And I was doing what
everyone else was doing

00:26:00.170 --> 00:26:03.890 align:middle line:84%
and why is it working
for them and not me?

00:26:03.890 --> 00:26:05.330 align:middle line:84%
And I remember
thinking about that

00:26:05.330 --> 00:26:07.040 align:middle line:90%
once when I was at a red light.

00:26:07.040 --> 00:26:10.510 align:middle line:84%
I was driving and I had
my little dog next to me.

00:26:10.510 --> 00:26:12.470 align:middle line:84%
