to the dog park.

00:26:12.470 --> 00:26:14.900 align:middle line:84%
And I was stopped at a red
light and for some reason

00:26:14.900 --> 00:26:16.610 align:middle line:90%
I'm thinking about this.

00:26:16.610 --> 00:26:18.380 align:middle line:84%
And I'm thinking, I
just don't understand.

00:26:18.380 --> 00:26:19.460 align:middle line:90%
I don't know what else to do.

00:26:19.460 --> 00:26:20.660 align:middle line:90%
How do I get to seven figures?

00:26:20.660 --> 00:26:21.868 align:middle line:90%
How does everyone else do it?

00:26:21.868 --> 00:26:24.380 align:middle line:84%
I'm doing exactly what they're
doing, it's not working,

00:26:24.380 --> 00:26:26.750 align:middle line:90%
I don't understand.

00:26:26.750 --> 00:26:30.110 align:middle line:84%
And then it got quiet in my
head for like five seconds.

00:26:30.110 --> 00:26:32.640 align:middle line:84%
And then the next
thought was this.

00:26:32.640 --> 00:26:35.210 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, but Sonia,
remember when you

00:26:35.210 --> 00:26:37.010 align:middle line:84%
