00:26:58.550 --> 00:26:59.780 align:middle line:90%
You have to let people go.

00:26:59.780 --> 00:27:03.440 align:middle line:84%
They start crying, you have to
deal with all that situation.

00:27:03.440 --> 00:27:05.210 align:middle line:84%
You don't want to
make seven figures.

00:27:05.210 --> 00:27:08.350 align:middle line:90%


00:27:08.350 --> 00:27:10.410 align:middle line:90%
That story popped into my head.

00:27:10.410 --> 00:27:12.910 align:middle line:84%
And I just remember, and I think
it's because I became aware

00:27:12.910 --> 00:27:15.220 align:middle line:90%
of my thoughts.

00:27:15.220 --> 00:27:18.550 align:middle line:84%
But this one was so deep that I
never noticed this one until I

00:27:18.550 --> 00:27:19.960 align:middle line:90%
was stopped at this red light.

00:27:19.960 --> 00:27:25.030 align:middle line:84%
And I go, did I just really
just say that to myself?

00:27:25.030 --> 00:27:26.200 align:middle line:90%
That's a limiting belief.

00:27:26.200 --> 00:27:28.843 align:middle line:84%
I had a limiting belief that
in order to make seven figures,

00:27:28.843 --> 00:27:30.010 align:middle line:90%
I'd have to have a big team.

00:27:30.010 --> 00:27:32.260 align:middle line:84%
And if I had a big team, I
would be really miserable.

00:27:32.260 --> 00:27:33.177 align:middle line:90%
Because you know what?

00:27:33.177 --> 00:27:36.070 align:middle line:90%
I was miserable in the past.

00:27:36.070 --> 00:27:38.240 align:middle line:90%
And that isn't true.

00:27:38.240 --> 00:27:41.920 align:middle line:84%
I know people, my colleagues who
have really small teams making

00:27:41.920 --> 00:27:43.660 align:middle line:90%
multiple seven figures.

00:27:43.660 --> 00:27:44.740 align:middle line:90%
So it wasn't even true.

00:27:44.740 --> 00:27:47.170 align:middle line:84%
It was a limiting belief
that I didn't even

00:27:47.170 --> 00:27:49.653 align:middle line:84%
realize I had until
I became aware of it.

00:27:49.653 --> 00:27:51.070 align:middle line:84%
So I took it from
the subconscious

00:27:51.070 --> 00:27:53.260 align:middle line:90%
and brought it to the conscious.

00:27:53.260 --> 00:27:55.900 align:middle line:84%
And then I laughed at myself
and I said, oh my goodness,

00:27:55.900 --> 00:27:58.270 align:middle line:90%
that's it.

00:27:58.270 --> 00:28:00.968 align:middle line:84%
I have been self-sabotaging
myself all along.

00:28:00.968 --> 00:28:03.010 align:middle line:84%
Because I really didn't
want that, because I knew

00:28:03.010 --> 00:28:05.410 align:middle line:90%
it would make me miserable.

00:28:05.410 --> 00:28:06.550 align:middle line:90%
When it wasn't even true.

00:28:06.550 --> 00:28:09.400 align:middle line:84%
So I thought, OK, well,
now my new belief is this.

00:28:09.400 --> 00:28:13.300 align:middle line:84%
