figures, multiple seven

00:28:13.300 --> 00:28:15.700 align:middle line:84%
figures, if possible,
that's ideal,

00:28:15.700 --> 00:28:17.740 align:middle line:84%
and I'm going to do
it with a small team

00:28:17.740 --> 00:28:19.480 align:middle line:84%
and it's going to
be my dream team.

00:28:19.480 --> 00:28:22.420 align:middle line:84%
And this dream team are
going to be super evolved,

00:28:22.420 --> 00:28:25.090 align:middle line:84%
inspirational, really
behind the mission,

00:28:25.090 --> 00:28:26.950 align:middle line:84%
and we will all love
each other and we're

00:28:26.950 --> 00:28:30.680 align:middle line:84%
going to work together and
make this world a better place.

00:28:30.680 --> 00:28:33.070 align:middle line:90%
Now that feels good.

00:28:33.070 --> 00:28:34.990 align:middle line:90%
And I continued driving.

00:28:34.990 --> 00:28:36.960 align:middle line:84%
And shortly after
that, everything

00:28:36.960 --> 00:28:37.960 align:middle line:90%
shifted in the business.

00:28:37.960 --> 00:28:40.860 align:middle line:90%


00:28:40.860 --> 00:28:44.430 align:middle line:84%
>> So that process for shifting
that limiting belief system

00:28:44.430 --> 00:28:48.300 align:middle line:84%
became from a subconscious
to a conscious process.

00:28:48.300 --> 00:28:50.410 align:middle line:90%
Powerful.

