00:29:58.340 --> 00:29:59.630 align:middle line:90%
that isn't working.

00:29:59.630 --> 00:30:00.710 align:middle line:90%
So let's say financial.

00:30:00.710 --> 00:30:03.135 align:middle line:84%
And then just write
out the story.

00:30:03.135 --> 00:30:04.010 align:middle line:90%
Write out your story.

00:30:04.010 --> 00:30:06.545 align:middle line:84%
Just hand write the story of
what's going on in that area.

00:30:06.545 --> 00:30:08.420 align:middle line:84%
