00:30:10.407 --> 00:30:12.740 align:middle line:84%
write and write and write and
write and write and write.

00:30:12.740 --> 00:30:13.820 align:middle line:90%
So you tell your story.

00:30:13.820 --> 00:30:16.520 align:middle line:84%
It's like, I can't believe
