noticing the story.

00:30:55.730 --> 00:30:57.500 align:middle line:90%
A, how negative it is.

00:30:57.500 --> 00:30:59.690 align:middle line:84%
And B, ask yourself
that question.

00:30:59.690 --> 00:31:02.120 align:middle line:84%
