and the thought did enter
my mind at one point, maybe

01:04:38.210 --> 01:04:41.250 align:middle line:84%
that is an option, but
I'm not giving up yet.

01:04:41.250 --> 01:04:46.950 align:middle line:84%
To going from being able
to, there was one day,

